<ns1:verse osisID="2Chr.29.8" sID="2Chr.29.8" /><ns1:w lemma="strong:H07110">Wherefore the wrath</ns1:w> <ns1:w lemma="strong:H03068">of the <ns1:seg><ns1:divineName>Lord</ns1:divineName></ns1:seg></ns1:w> <ns1:w lemma="strong:H03063">was upon Judah</ns1:w> <ns1:w lemma="strong:H03389">and Jerusalem</ns1:w>, <ns1:w morph="strongMorph:TH8799" lemma="strong:H05414">and he hath delivered</ns1:w> <ns1:w morph="strongMorph:TH8675" lemma="strong:H02113 strong:H02189">them to trouble</ns1:w>, <ns1:w lemma="strong:H08047">to astonishment</ns1:w>, <ns1:w lemma="strong:H08322">and to hissing</ns1:w>, <ns1:w morph="strongMorph:TH8802" lemma="strong:H07200">as ye see</ns1:w> <ns1:w lemma="strong:H05869">with your eyes</ns1:w>.<ns1:note type="study">trouble: Heb. commotion</ns1:note><ns1:verse eID="2Chr.29.8" />
